originalText.text: This place has Absolutely no idea what customer service means....I walked in with a Government check for $81.00 & presented my proper photo ID & expected to be walking out in a minute or two....This young kid behind the glass tells me that the check is over 1 week old (8 days) & therefore can't & won't cash the check....The most Unprofessional service I've ever experienced in a check cashing establishment..... Didn't even try to explain why , just go to the the one you usually go to and they will cash it for me...... RIDICULOUS ! WHAT A MAJOR LEAGUE DOUCHEBAG !
